Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In response to the cowardly act of the Terrans\Nwho turned on Princess Asseylum,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who came down to Earth in order to\Nmake herself a bridge of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we Orbital Knights must\Ndeal them a crushing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Terrans' spilled blood will be\Nour tribute to Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, keep it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was a nervous wreck! I thought I was\Ngoing to step on you, Matsuribi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you had, you'd get hit with a\Nlot worse than point deductions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't even funny,\Nright, Yutaro-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd stop\Ncalling me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you climb down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The landing craft's radar has picked up\Nmultiple massive bodies above Shinawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A meteor bombardment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Freaking Martians!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We made it out just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you, Eddelrittuo.\NHow go things here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No change, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good work out there, Nao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's due entirely to the guidance of your\Ngood-natured, beautiful instructor, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You came to rescue us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When I didn't see your names on\Nthe ferries' passenger manifests, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a relief, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The city is gone, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way. We're gonna survive this,\Nmark my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then maybe you should start\Nby dodging that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right? Left?\NRight? Right? Left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quick exhaust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, what's the helmsman doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for earlier, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho. Inaho Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Inaho. I am-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, call me Seylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that, Seylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it is not too much trouble, perhaps\Nyou could show me around the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Milady, you-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us try that again. I am\NAsseylum Vers Allusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor Vers' granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the real you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My earlier appearance is the\Nresult of what I am told
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is a form of optical camouflage\Nthat employs holography.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The princess was assassinated on the day\Nof the parade. I saw the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A double.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness was not\Nfeeling well that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, the skeptical security detail\Nleader insisted that a double be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that wasn't a hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When my grandfather the emperor\Nlearns that I am alive and well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this war will come to\Nan end immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to get in touch with\NVers as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, it would be\Ndifficult to do from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their jamming makes long-range\Ncommunications impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:07:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And our telecommunications bases have been\Ndestroyed, so we can't use the Net, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we can take you to a facility that\Ncan contact the Vers government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to my sister Yuki\Nand the others about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a Vers spy hidden\Namongst the Terrans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In league with those assassins, no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The spy wishes to see\NHer Highness dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize for dragging you\Ninto our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, keep this\Nmatter between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad that we\Nhave you here, Dr. Yagarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't used exoskeleton\Ntherapy in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please refrain from doing anything crazy.\NThis is only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll do, it'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you aren't in pain doesn't mean\Nthere isn't any strain on your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When that anesthetic wears off,\Nit's going to be unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it, don't worry. I'll come in\Nfor fine-tuning later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe I should have you make a few\Nmore adjustments while you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so Okisuke was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he was a moron\Nup to the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A moron and a perv\Nand a slacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poor bastard, dying and then\Ngetting chewed out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't have\Ngotten himself killed, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They started a war\Nand destroyed the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Fall wrecked the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've been up there in the Satellite Belt\Nlooking down on us ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them pay! For Okojo and\Nevery other Terran who was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Martian sons of bitches...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?\NKeep her secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In an extreme situation where there's\Nno telling when an enemy will come,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,human beings aren't known for\Nremaining calm and rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they found out that she's a Martian, there's\Nno telling what might happen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real softie, aren't you?\NShowing concern for the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is the people who\Ntried to assassinate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If what she says is true, we need to deliver\Nher... Seylum, safely to United Earth HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rayet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name.\NIt's Rayet Areash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Rayet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make no guarantees.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I think we're in danger,\NI'll spill everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Martians are all the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Trillram... is dead, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord. He was caught\Nin the meteor bombardment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Swine... To think one of us would target my\Noccupied territory under the cover of the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have they no honor as a fellow\NOrbital Knight with a common goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Sooner or later, I shall uncover\Nhis identity and mete out his punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summon Vlad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hunt down the remnant Terrans\Nand burn this place to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We shall avenge\NHer Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Princess Asseylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I'm going to kill her\Nand make certain this time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, Milord. Inflicting further devastation\Nupon a previously conquered area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Given Princess Asseylum's sentiments,\Nmight that not be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You imply that you wish to\Nhave some say in avenging her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, Terran!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think yourself worthy of\Ndoing battle at Vers' side?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For 15 long years, we Orbital Knights\Ningloriously looked out at the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from the shattered Moon, yearning for the\Nday we would reach out and take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With her death, the Princess has made\Nthat cherished dream a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This battle belongs to the Orbital Knights.\NIt is no concern of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's trying to exploit\Nthe Princess' death, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trillram was an invited guest\Nat Castle Cruhteo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we let her live, my entire clan and its\Nfollowers will be branded as traitors!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"We"... This assassination\Nconspiracy has a ringleader.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Count Cruhteo?\NNo, it couldn't be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Power down engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Power down engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Magbaredge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe!\NWe've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Nakabayashi. Good work.\NWhere's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The amphibious assault craft Wadatsumi is\Ncurrently taking a longer, safer route.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The seas are a mess thanks\Nto that meteor bombardment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On XO Mizusaki's orders, we went ahead\Nin Craft #1 with Appaloosa Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are here to support you and defend the\Nrefugees until the Wadatsumi arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still... this place was\Nabandoned, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's been no\Ndamage to this area yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Digging in only makes the damage worse.\NThe best thing is to bug out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly the opinion I'd expect from someone\Nwho lived through the war 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait for the Wadatsumi to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have anyone who isn't busy help with\Nresupplying the landing craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave your rations here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual for you\Nto offer to help out, Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you always played hooky\Nfrom military drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll do anything if it means\Nwiping out the Martians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've set up a three-shift\Nperimeter watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any word from\Nthe Wadatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, the jamming's too intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe a signal can't\Ncross a few dozen miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue scanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Appaloosa Leader,\Nthis is Appaloosa 33.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have located friendly unit.\NAppears to be damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the matter,\NAppaloosa 33?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All hands to battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.\NPrep Craft #1 for liftoff ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get inside, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Appaloosa 33, sitrep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enemy Kataphrakts, 1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding behind building.\NCurrently engaging.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surround it and fire at will.\NAll units, spread out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Projectile weapons?\NHow crude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Witness the power of my\Ncustomized Kataphrakt, the Argyre!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah output climbing.\NConnecting to energy joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deploying blade field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah drive output at maximum.\NPlasma generator startup preparations complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sword drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of laser weapon?\NNo... It's a katana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Appaloosa 33!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Message from Craft #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Captain Magbaredge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Status?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good, ma'am.\NHow about on your end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fueling complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Refugee boarding complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lift off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get some distance and\Nfinish this with SSMs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's regroup out at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Mars Knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sitrep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damage to hull! Negligible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will not affect seaworthiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APU shutting down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to power up engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The main engine looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make temporary repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the same type\Nas the one this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That thing in its hand...\NIs that a beam katana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall speak with\Nthat knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mila-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous! What if he is\Nin league with the assassins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware of the risk. But that is\Nthe only way to keep everyone safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! You were lucky\Nthis afternoon, nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must never do something\Nso reckless again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy us some time.\NYou two get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're your friends, aren't we?\NWe'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko, I need you up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Up where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trainers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engine room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're patching straight\Ninto the pressure tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No luck with HE rounds, huh?\NThen let's try AP rounds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clever. Rounds that contain no\Nexplosives won't detonate in midair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tips are evaporating and throwing\Noff the bullets' trajectory...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Leidenfrost effect, huh?\NThe heat it's putting out is incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pincer attack, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How amusing. But how long can\Nyou last in that Kataphrakt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little more\Nto the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My main monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you insects\Nthink you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry we're late,\NCaptain Magbaredge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It took a long time to\Nfind a safe route.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki, would you like to know\Nwhy you can't get a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought you were supposed to\Narrive fashionably late, ma'am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a tactic that you use\Nafter you've landed a date.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke's cleared!\NNow able to target!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disable fuses on rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kataphrakt Platoon, take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have pressure!\NTurbine RPMs climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can get away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not worth my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly as planned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What plan?! That was really\Nclose back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to be\Nso reckless, Inaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to avenge\NPrincess Asseylum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, I told you\Nthat you are not worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, Terran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...go into battle!
